26:47.096 --> 26:48.998
We must learn to follow.

26:49.038 --> 26:50.379
What it says in Psalm 37.

26:50.399 --> 26:52.661
Oh, this is good.

26:53.202 --> 26:55.184
The Lord directs the steps of the God.

