43:05.405 --> 43:06.306
I've got the call.

43:08.209 --> 43:09.390
Will you accept it?

43:12.534 --> 43:16.640
What we're building is for the next generation.

43:18.002 --> 43:21.687
What we're building is to reach those outside of these walls.

43:22.948 --> 43:27.314
What we're building is so that more people will go to heaven.

43:28.226 --> 43:30.348
I don't know about you, but I wanna populate heaven.

43:31.289 --> 43:40.139
We've learned over the last several weeks that there are like 69,000 people in our three counties of encountered church that are lost without Jesus Christ.

43:41.681 --> 43:43.583
I wanna see us make a dent in that.

43:44.705 --> 43:52.493
I'll be great to reach 69,000 people, but if we can just reach 10% of that, come on.

43:54.856 --> 43:56.658
We have got to build

43:57.122 --> 43:57.963
His church.

43:59.626 --> 44:05.715
And I'm gonna challenge, I'm gonna invite you to go with us on this journey.

44:07.779 --> 44:12.827
Not to be satisfied with just coming in on a Sunday morning and sitting.

44:12.867 --> 44:19.016
And I love you being here, but I believe God's called you to something more.

44:21.040 --> 44:22.642
Grow track is your next step.

44:23.778 --> 44:24.799
We've got that today.

44:24.900 --> 44:27.103
We've got it the first Sunday of every month, but I want to challenge you.

44:27.123 --> 44:27.663
Don't put it off.

44:28.184 --> 44:31.389
Some of you right now, first, when I said, grow check, you're like, okay, I could go to that.

44:31.649 --> 44:34.673
And then I said, hey, we have it the first month, our first Sunday every month.

44:34.693 --> 44:35.975
You went, okay, I'll wait till next month.

44:36.716 --> 44:40.041
No, because what'll happen is next month, you'll go, I'll wait till the next month.

44:40.721 --> 44:42.364
And the next month, you say, I'll wait till the next month.

44:42.544 --> 44:45.348
When life slows down, then I'll do it.

44:48.733 --> 44:48.993
Today.

44:49.954 --> 44:50.695
I want to challenge you.

44:50.896 --> 44:52.658
Just, let's flood that room today.

44:54.562 --> 44:57.586
It's going to start here in about 15 minutes.

44:59.188 --> 45:02.493
That gives you time to grab another coffee and go head on.

45:02.513 --> 45:04.255
It's just right here to the left.

45:05.437 --> 45:06.478
But that's your next step.

45:08.081 --> 45:12.146
And those of you that are in ministry, I want to challenge you to duplicate yourself.

45:14.049 --> 45:17.413
Well, Pastor, if I duplicate myself, what happens if they start doing it better than me?

45:17.433 --> 45:17.974
Great!

45:19.396 --> 45:20.698
Then I'll find something else for you.

45:20.778 --> 45:23.762
Right?

45:24.578 --> 45:25.840
We're not building our church.

45:27.322 --> 45:28.364
We're building his church.

45:31.027 --> 45:32.189
Would you buy your heads with me today?

45:34.733 --> 45:36.395
God, we thank you right now for who you are.

45:38.358 --> 45:41.563
Let me thank you, Lord, that we can lean into you.

45:43.045 --> 45:45.829
Lord, that we don't have to do the building process by ourselves.

45:47.532 --> 45:54.482
Let me thank you, God, that you've already set the course, that you delight in every detail of our lives.

45:55.330 --> 45:59.436
Lord, help us, Lord, to be obedience to your call.

46:01.159 --> 46:04.905
Lord, help us to build your church, not ours, but yours.

46:07.108 --> 46:18.225
As we dig down and deep, as we root ourselves into the foundation, Lord, help us to wholly depend upon you in Jesus' name.

46:19.207 --> 46:19.527
Amen.

46:19.567 --> 46:21.490
With your heads bowed and your eyes closed.

